Pronunciation: \Surge ee-BAK-ah\

Serge Ibaka ▪ Instagram: sergeibaka

(Full name Serge Jonas Ibaka Ngobila)

(Air Congo, Mafuzzy Chef, Iblaka)

NBA Debut: October 30, 2009

Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Serge Ibaka?

Serge Ibaka is 35 years old.

Where was Serge Ibaka born?

Serge Ibaka was born in Brazzaville, Congo.

When was Serge Ibaka born?

Serge Ibaka was born on September 18, 1989.

How tall is Serge Ibaka?

Serge Ibaka is 6-11 (211 cm) tall.

How much did Serge Ibaka weigh when playing?

Serge Ibaka weighed 235 lbs (106 kg) when playing.

Is Serge Ibaka in the Hall of Fame?

Serge Ibaka is not in the Hall of Fame.

When was Serge Ibaka drafted?

Serge Ibaka was drafted by Seattle SuperSonics, 1st round (24th pick, 24th overall), 2008 NBA Draft.

What position did Serge Ibaka play?

Power Forward and Center.

When did Serge Ibaka retire?

Serge Ibaka last played in 2023.

What is Serge Ibaka's net worth?

Serge Ibaka made at least $140,880,652 playing professional basketball.

How much did Serge Ibaka make?

Serge Ibaka made $23,271,604 in 2020.

What did Serge Ibaka average?

Serge Ibaka averaged 12.0 points, 7.1 rebounds, and 0.8 assists per game.

How many rings does Serge Ibaka have?

Serge Ibaka won one championship.
